short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Preview of what the GitHub developer's page would have looked like, if he had done his job earlier.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a pure entertainment extension, focused on developers, who want to see how a certain GitHub page would look if most of the fields are filled in with information. The idea is to cheer up and motivate Junior Developers while looking for their next adventure.
